{"search_data": "CentralNational SC/ST Hub \u2013 Facilitating SC/ST Entrepreneurs in MSME SectorUnder the scheme, the nationalized banks will provide loans to SC/ST men and women entrepreneurs up to Rs. 1 Crore to make them self dependent and employ the youth.The SC/ST hub will further help in increasing the contributions of MSME sector to India\u2019s GDP which is about 38% at present. The MSME sector employs about 11 Crore people at present. The announcement of setting up the National SC/ST hub was made by the finance minister Shri Arun Jaitly in his budget speech of 2016-17.The scheme will be implemented by the Ministry of Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises. More information about the National SC/ST hub can be viewed on the official website of ministry at http://msme.gov.in/mob/home.aspx  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}